<a href=http://pub61.ezboard.com/bsaryrnfamiljen><font color=blue>Familjen Saryrn</font></a><BR>
<img src=http://home.houston.rr.com/dnaae/Rolalogo.gif></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umissfoxfyre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Miss Foxfyre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Gardener in the Grove<br>Admin au naturel</span><br>  Posts: 2245<br> <font color=#333399>(7/31/02 9:40:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26457.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.cityviewsoftware.com/jennifer/small.jpg HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=84></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Girdle of Magnificence</span><hr size=1> Two groups, I'd say. <br>
<br>
Lcea was one of the first long fights I did some time after Luclin's release. Three groups can get her for sure; two was on-the-edge fun. :p I didn't find her charm particularly strong. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugwynetwoodsister.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gwynet Woodsister</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Watcher of the Grove</span><br>  Posts: 487<br> <font color=#333399>(8/1/02 6:01:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26457.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Girdle of Magnificence</span><hr size=1> They buffed her. It used to be a two groups thing, now she can charm up to 3 or 4 people at the same time (pretty hard to resist even with 160 MR) and she hits for 750 or so (I can't remember exactly). It gets ugly very fast.<br>
<br>
We killed her a few times before that, then we stopped because the risk is no longer worth the reward. <p><font face=verdena><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1972">Leorny Nukite</a>, Grandmaster<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1974">
Nilenya</a>, Phantasmist<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1971">Gwynet Woodsister</a>, Hierophant<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4239">
Sylina Uthmatar</a>, 43 Shadowknight<br>
Valiant Elite, Druzzil-Ro</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ul1ndara.showPublicProfile?language=EN>L1ndara</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Puppy</span><br>  Posts: 57<br> <font color=#333399>(8/2/02 7:58:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26457.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Girdle of Magnificence</span><hr size=1>   Hehe yeah and when they buffed her she went from a wimpy red con to a somewhat nasty white con.  We just can't kill her without deaths anymore, she has undead agro and charm means EVERYONE will likely get their turn on the agro list and 1 flurry and it's over. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showPrevMessage?topicID=26457.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showNextMessage?topicID=26457.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26457.topic&index=6><img src=http://dev.thedruidsgrove.org/images/forum/addreplya.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.emailToFriend?topicID=26457.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.threadControl?topicID=26457.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <